{
  "stem": "15174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were standing in back of the crowd and they were just watching this and doing absolutely nothing to prevent it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Soon after that, I remember going to synagogue with my father on Saturday morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We used to walk to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's one of the nice memories I have of my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We walked together to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember we were walking on some of the streets in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And again I saw a lot of stores with broken windows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And of course, they were Jewish stores which had been broken into.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "All of this-- you know, and I-- I understood in one way or another as a young kid that this was aimed at Jews and I was Jewish and so it was aimed at me.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was very scary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- you know, I was upset about this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was afraid to go on the street by myself certainly, but even with my parents I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So it was-- it was not pleasant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "On the other hand, there were some nice things too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I mean, I remember the whole family went on picnics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "My-- my father's brother lived in Berlin, he and his wife and two daughters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And his two sisters also lived in Berlin, Rose and Frieda.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Frieda was married to Alan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She had a daughter Edith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the-- my three cousins, the three girls, we were about-- you know, pretty close in age, so we were really good friends.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Used to go on picnics.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And one summer we actually went to the North Sea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I-- I don't remember actually swimming, but I remember being on a boat with my parents and my uncle.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And actually, we have a picture of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
